Subject: Issue with License Release Not Reflecting
Description: I am from the InfoSec team. I tried to release the license for a specific user and submitted the request. It showed that the license was successfully released, but the count remains the same. Even after refreshing and checking again, the license is still not released.
What_We_Know__c: Released license and saved the license release to be done at 30 days.
